'''深紫'''（{{lang-en|'''Deep Purple'''}}）是[[英國|英國]]的[[硬式搖滾|硬式搖滾]]／[[重金屬音樂|重金屬]]樂團，1968年成立於英國[[哈特福_(英國)|哈特福]]<ref>《{{link-en|深紫色調|Shades of Deep Purple}}》專輯手冊註記（1968），第4–5頁</ref>。樂團被認為是重金屬音樂和現代硬式搖滾的開拓者之一<ref name="Wasler">Robert Wasler《Running with the Devil: power, gender, and madness in heavy metal music》{{link-en|衛斯理大學出版社|Wesleyan University Press}}（1993）ISBN 0-8195-6260-2，第10頁</ref><ref name="Campbell">Michael Campbell、James Brody《Rock and Roll: An Introduction》Schirmer（2008）ISBN 978-0534642952，第213頁</ref>。樂團的風格曾幾次的異動過<ref>{{cite news|language = en|author=Jeb Wright |url=http://www.classicrockrevisited.com/interviewIANGILLAN09.htm |title=The Naked Truth: An Exclusive Interview with Deep Purple’s Ian Gillan |work=Classic Rock Revisited |year=2009 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090427152050/http://www.classicrockrevisited.com/interviewIANGILLAN09.htm |archivedate=2009-04-27 }}</ref>，成立之初是[[前衛搖滾|前衛搖滾]]，在1970年轉向重金屬風格<ref name="Charlton">Katherine Charlton《Rock Music Styles: A History》[[麥格羅-希爾集團|麥格羅-希爾集團]]（2014）ISBN 978-0078025181，第241頁</ref>。深紫與[[黑色安息日|黑色安息日]]、[[齊柏林飛船_(樂團)|齊柏林飛船]]被視為「重金屬音樂的三大元老」<ref>{{link-en|Joel McIver|Joel McIver}}《Sabbath Bloody Sabbath》{{link-en|Omnibus Press|Omnibus Press}}（2007）ISBN 978-1844499823，第1頁</ref>。根據1975年《[[金氏世界紀錄大全|金氏世界紀錄大全]]》記載，深紫於1972年在[[倫敦|倫敦]]{{link-en|彩虹劇院|Rainbow Theatre}}的演出創下「{{link-en|世界上音量最大聲的樂團|Loudest band}}」紀錄<ref>Ross McWhirter《Guinness Book of World Records》{{link-en|Sterling Publishing|Sterling Publishing}}（1975）ISBN 978-0-8069-0012-4，第242頁</ref><ref name="Jason Ankeny">{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/deep-purple-p4061/biography |title=Deep Purple |author=Jason Ankeny |work=[[Allmusic|Allmusic]] |accessdate=2011-12-24 |archive-date=2011-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110929200021/http://www.allmusic.com/artist/deep-purple-p4061/biography |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他們在全球銷售了超過一億張唱片<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://m.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2174437/Jon-Lord-dead-71-cancer-Deep-Purple-founder-wrote-Smoke-On-The-Water-dies.html |title=Deep Purple founder who co-wrote classics including Smoke On The Water dies at 71 |work=[[每日郵報|每日郵報]] |accessdate=2012-07-25 |archive-date=2020-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200324193241/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2174437/Jon-Lord-dead-71-cancer-Deep-Purple-founder-wrote-Smoke-On-The-Water-dies.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2012/07/16/showbiz/jon-lord-obit/index.html |title=Jon Lord, keyboard player with seminal hard rock act Deep Purple, dies |work=[[CNN|CNN]] |accessdate=2012-07-25 |archive-date=2021-02-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210210204118/https://edition.cnn.com/2012/07/16/showbiz/jon-lord-obit/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/culturevideo/musicvideo/9404573/Deep-Purple-keyboard-player-Jon-Lord-dies-aged-71.html |title=Deep Purple keyboard player Jon Lord dies aged 71 |work=[[每日電訊報|每日電訊報]] |accessdate=2012-07-25 |archive-date=2013-02-25 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6EhgmooWJ?url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/culturevideo/musicvideo/9404573/Deep-Purple-keyboard-player-Jon-Lord-dies-aged-71.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

深紫的陣容經歷過多次改變，並且在1976年解散（成員陣容普遍被分為Mark I、II、III、IV、V、VI、VII和VIII），中斷了八年後在1984年重組<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.rock.co.za/files/marki.html |title=Deep Purple Mark I & Mark II |work=rock.co |accessdate=2017-02-20 |archive-date=2010-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100327213958/http://rock.co.za/files/marki.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。他們在商業上最成功的陣容是“Mark II”時，{{link-en|伊恩·吉蘭|Ian Gillan}}（主唱），[[瓊·洛德|瓊·洛德]]（鍵盤手），{{link-en|羅傑·格洛弗|Roger Glover}}（貝斯手），{{link-en|伊恩·佩斯|Ian Paice}}（鼓手）和[[瑞奇·布萊克摩爾|瑞奇·布萊克摩爾]]（吉他手）。這個陣容活躍於1969年至1973年、並從1984年重組到1989年、以及1992年到1993年間。目前的陣容是伊恩·佩斯（鼓手），羅傑·格洛弗（貝斯手），伊恩·吉蘭（主唱），{{link-en|史提夫·莫爾斯|Steve Morse}}（吉他手）和{{link-en|唐·艾瑞|Don Airey}}（鍵盤手）。其中伊恩·佩斯是唯一一位乐團的創始成員。

[[美國|美國]][[VH1|VH1]]將深紫列為「百大優秀硬搖滾樂團」第22名<ref>{{cite web|language=en|url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/vh1-counts-down-the-100-greatest-artists-of-hard-rock-in-five-hour-five-night-special-premiering-november-13-17-at-1000-pm-etpt-75380612.html|title=VH1 Counts Down the '100 Greatest Artists of Hard Rock' In Five-Hour, Five-Night Special|work=[[美通社|美通社]]|accessdate=2015-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121025064126/http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/vh1-counts-down-the-100-greatest-artists-of-hard-rock-in-five-hour-five-night-special-premiering-november-13-17-at-1000-pm-etpt-75380612.html|archive-date=2012-10-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。在英國廣播電台{{link-en|搖滾星球 (電台)|Planet Rock (radio station)|搖滾星球}}的調查中，他們在「歷來最有影響力的樂團」排行第5位<ref>{{cite web|language=en|url=http://www.planetrock.com/promotions/most-influential-rock-band-poll/planet-rock-poll-most-influential-band-ever-the-results/|title=Planet Rock: Most Influential Band EVER – The Results.|work={{link-en|搖滾星球 (電台)|Planet Rock (radio station)|搖滾星球}}|accessdate=2013-02-25|archive-date=2020-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200122141005/https://www.planetrock.com/promotions/most-influential-rock-band-poll/planet-rock-poll-most-influential-band-ever-the-results/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。深紫在2005年獲得[[世界音樂獎|世界音樂獎]]「傳奇獎」<ref name="WMA">{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.worldmusicawards.com/index.php/awards/ |title=World Music Awards: Legends |accessdate=2015-09-09 |work=[[世界音樂獎|世界音樂獎]] |archive-date=2015-08-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150828112443/http://www.worldmusicawards.com/index.php/awards |dead-url=no }}</ref>、2011年獲{{link-en|經典搖滾獎|Classic Rock Roll of Honour Awards}}「創新獎」<ref name="CRAward">{{cite web|language=en|url=http://www.classicrockmagazine.com/news/cr-awards-the-winners/|title=CR AWARDS: The Winners|work={{link-en|經典搖滾 (雜誌)|Classic Rock (magazine)|經典搖滾}}|accessdate=2012-06-17|archive-date=2014-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140403183209/http://www.classicrockmagazine.com/news/cr-awards-the-winners/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並且在2016年入選[[搖滾名人堂|搖滾名人堂]]<ref name="2016 RHOF">{{cite web|language=en|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/deep-purple-rocks-hall-of-fame-with-hits-filled-set-20160408|title=Deep Purple Rocks Hall of Fame With Hits-Filled Set|work=[[滾石_(雜誌)|滾石 (雜誌)]]|accessdate=2016-10-19|archive-date=2017-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201034440/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/deep-purple-rocks-hall-of-fame-with-hits-filled-set-20160408|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 歷史 ==
=== 組建（1967 - 1968年） ===
1967年，前搖滾樂團{{link-en|搜索者 (樂團)|The Searchers (band)|搜索者}}的鼓手{{link-en|克里斯·柯提斯|Chris Curtis}}找上倫敦的服飾商人{{link-en|東尼·愛德華|Tony Edwards}}，說服他資助自己要組的新樂團「圓環」（意即成員可自由加入或退出），他的想法類似[[超級樂團|超級樂團]]，這讓愛德華決定為他籌措資金，並另外找來兩位生意夥伴{{link-en|約翰·科萊塔|John Coletta}}和{{link-en|朗·海爾|Ron Hire}}合資成立了HEC企業<ref name="Thompson">{{link-en|Dave Thompson|Dave Thompson (author)}}《Smoke on the Water: The Deep Purple Story》{{link-en|ECW Press|ECW Press}}（2004）ISBN 978-1-55022-618-8，第27頁</ref>。

第一位招募的成員是鍵盤手[[瓊·洛德|瓊·洛德]]，他擅長鋼琴、[[管風琴|管風琴]]和[[電子琴|電子琴]]，以及[[古典音樂|古典音樂]]、[[巴洛克音樂|巴洛克音樂]]、[[爵士樂|爵士樂]]和[[藍調|藍調]]，當時因為與[[滾石樂隊|滾石樂隊]]吉他手的弟弟{{link-en|亞特·伍德|Art Wood}}玩團而頗有名氣<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/the-artwoods-mn0000033079 |title=The Artwoods |author=Bruce Eder |work=Allmusic |accessdate=2011-12-12 |archive-date=2020-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200903065518/https://www.allmusic.com/artist/the-artwoods-mn0000033079 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。接著加入的是著名搖滾樂團{{link-en|強尼·基德與海盜|Johnny Kidd and The Pirates}}的前成員：貝斯手{{link-en|尼克·辛博|Nick Simper}}和鼓手{{link-en|卡羅·雷托|Carlo Little}}。之後辛博提議招攬在英[[德國|德]]兩地名聲鹤立的優秀吉他手[[瑞奇·布萊克摩爾|瑞奇·布萊克摩爾]]<ref name="darker">{{cite web | language = en | url = http://www.nicksimper.com/nick_simper_interview_july83.htm | title = Nick Simper Interview from "Darker than Blue", July 1983 | accessdate = 2014-01-15 | last = Robinson | first = Simon | date = 1983-07-02 | work = Darker than Blue | publisher = Nick Simper official website | archive-date = 2006-11-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20061120144157/http://www.nicksimper.com/nick_simper_interview_july83.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。因為辛博很早以前就和布萊克摩爾的樂團共演過<ref>Dave Thompson《Smoke on the Water: The Deep Purple Story》ECW Press（2004）ISBN 978-1-55022-618-8，第5頁</ref>。

1967年12月，愛德華說服布萊克摩爾同意加入「圓環」。然而這時柯提斯卻因為[[麥角酸二乙醯胺|LSD]]成癮，導致行為及情緒不穩定，他逐漸失去了組建樂團的興趣，於是HEC企業將他解僱。三位股東對樂團的巨大潜力和未來非常樂觀，並未撤資。而且洛德和布萊克摩爾兩人一拍即合，也希望繼續合作<ref name="Curtis">{{cite web |language = en| url = http://www.allmusic.com/artist/chris-curtis-p67960/biography | title = Chris Curtis Biograph | accessdate = 2014-01-15 | last = Thompson | first = Dave| publisher = Allmusic}}</ref>。雷托在此時退出，洛德提議讓{{link-en|巴比·伍德曼|Bobby Woodman}}接任鼓手<ref name="darker"/>。

1968年3月，四位成員（洛德、布萊克摩爾、辛博、伍德曼）搬到[[赫特福德郡|赫特福郡]]的一棟鄉間別墅<ref>Dafydd Rees、Luke Crampton《VH1 Rock Stars Encyclopedia》[[多林金德斯利|多林金德斯利]]（1999）ISBN 978-0789446138，第279頁</ref><ref>Pete Frame《Pete Frame's Rockin' Around Britain: Rock'n'roll Landmarks of the UK and Ireland》Omnibus Press（1999）ISBN 978-0711969735，第54頁</ref>。樂團在此生活、寫歌與練團。他們整裝待發，使用{{link-en|馬歇爾音箱公司|Marshall Amplification}}最新型的設備、還有全新的樂器<ref name="Bloom">{{cite book |language=en |author=Jerry Bloom |year=2006 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=FcKcrWE8aWgC&pg=PT163 |title=Black Knight: Ritchie Blackmore |publisher=Omnibus Press 2008 |quote=Blackmore has stated; "It was a song my grandmother used to play on the piano." |access-date=2017-02-20 |archive-date=2020-07-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200731133044/https://books.google.com/books?id=FcKcrWE8aWgC&pg=PT163 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。根據辛博回憶，當時試音了「數十位」候選人，包括當時23歲的[[洛·史都華|洛·史都華]]和{{link-en|麥可·哈里森 (音樂家)|Mike Harrison (musician)|麥可·哈里森}}都去試過。但一直到聽見「迷宮」前主唱{{link-en|羅德·艾文斯|Rod Evans}}的歌聲、才認為找到一個風格比較適合樂團的主唱。陪艾文斯一起來面試的還有他樂團的鼓手{{link-en|伊恩·佩斯|Ian Paice}}，布萊克摩爾1966年在德國時見過「迷宮」演出，當年18歲的佩斯給他留下過深刻印象。碰巧當時伍德曼對音樂風格上的不滿意，於是樂團倉促的為佩斯安排一個鼓試音<ref name="darker"/>。最終，樂團錄取了艾文斯和佩斯，完成五人編制的陣容，日後被樂界稱為「Mark I」<ref name="autogenerated1983">Chris Welch《The Story of Deep Purple》（Deep Purple: HM Photo Book）Omnibus Press（1983）ISBN 978-0711902756</ref>。

1968年4月，「圓環」到[[丹麥|丹麥]]和[[瑞典|瑞典]]進行短暫巡演的途中，布萊克摩爾以一首奶奶最喜歡的歌曲名字為靈感，提議將團名「圓環」改成「深紫」<ref name="Curtis"/><ref name="Bloom"/>。經過全體投票後，樂團正式改名<ref>Dave Wilson《Rock Formations: Categorical Answers To How Band Names Were Formed》Cidermill Books（2005）ISBN 978-0974848358，第53頁</ref><ref name="archive">{{cite web | language = en | url = http://www.deep-purple.net/archive/68-76history/roundabout.htm | title = On The Roundabout With Deep Purple | accessdate = 2017-02-20 | last = Tyler | first = Kieron | publisher = deep-purple.net | archive-date = 2011-08-22 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/617rmrLyk?url=http://www.deep-purple.net/archive/68-76history/roundabout.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

