nguage=en|url=http://www.blabbermouth.net/news/ian-paice-deep-purple-hasnt-decided-yet-if-long-goodbye-will-be-bands-last-big-tour/|title=IAN PAICE: DEEP PURPLE Hasn't Decided Yet If 'Long Goodbye' Will Be Band's Last Big Tour|publisher=Blabbermouth.net|date=2017-01-20|accessdate=2017-01-22|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125201414/https://www.blabbermouth.net/news/ian-paice-deep-purple-hasnt-decided-yet-if-long-goodbye-will-be-bands-last-big-tour/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

