n|publisher=Allmusic|date=2017-01-20|accessdate=2012-02-22|archive-date=2012-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120211141153/http://www.allmusic.com/artist/van-halen-p133911|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[愛麗絲囚徒|愛麗絲囚徒]]<ref>{{cite web|language=en|author=Erlewine, Stephen Thomas|url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/alice-in-chains-p3520|title=Alice in Chains|publisher=Allmusic|date=2017-01-20|accessdate=2012-02-22|archive-date=2012-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120207093653/http://allmusic.com/artist/alice-in-chains-p3520|dead-url=no}}</ref>、{{link-en|潘特拉|Pantera}}<ref>{{cite web|language=en|author=Birchmeier, Jason|url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/pantera-p5099|title=Pantera|publisher=Allmusic|date=2017-01-20|accessdate=2012-02-26|archive-date=2012-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120529072226/http://www.allmusic.com/artist/pantera-p5099/|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[X_JAPAN|X JAPAN]]<ref name="rock7356925">{{Cite web|language=en|author=Natasha Scharf|title=Who the hell are X Japan?|url=http://teamrock.com/feature/2014-08-13/who-the-hell-are-x-japan|publisher=TeamRock|date=2014-08-13|accessdate=2017-02-25|archive-date=2017-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170225205605/http://teamrock.com/feature/2014-08-13/who-the-hell-are-x-japan|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[邦喬飛|邦喬飛]]<ref>{{cite web|language=en|author=Erlewine, Stephen Thomas|url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/bon-jovi-p3734|title=Bon Jovi|publisher=Allmusic|date=2017-01-20|accessdate=2012-02-22|archive-date=2012-05-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120527131505/http://www.allmusic.com/artist/bon-jovi-p3734/|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[歐洲合唱團|歐洲合唱團]]<ref>{{cite web|language=en|url=http://www.metal-rules.com/metalnews/2013/01/09/europe-interview-with-joey-tempest/|title=Europe – Interview with Joey Tempest|publisher=metal-rules.com|date=2017-01-20|accessdate=2014-03-23|archive-date=2017-05-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170530085039/http://www.metal-rules.com/metalnews/2013/01/09/europe-interview-with-joey-tempest/|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[匆促樂團|匆促樂團]]<ref>{{cite web|language=en|author=Ankeny, Jason|url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/rush-p5323|title=Rush|publisher=Allmusic|date=2017-01-20|accessdate=2012-02-26|archive-date=2011-12-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111229010827/http://www.allmusic.com/artist/rush-p5323/|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[摩托頭|摩托頭]]<ref>{{cite web|language=en|author=Erlewine, Stephen Thomas|url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/motrhead-p4965|title=Motorhead|publisher=Allmusic|date=2017-01-20|accessdate=2012-02-22|archive-date=2012-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120502000058/http://www.allmusic.com/artist/motrhead-p4965/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，以及許多[[英國重金屬新浪潮|英國重金屬新浪潮]]中的領導樂團，如[[鐵娘子樂團|鐵娘子]]<ref>{{cite web|language=en|author=Erlewine, Stephen Thomas|url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/iron-maiden-p4560|title=Iron Maiden|publisher=Allmusic|date=2017-01-20|accessdate=2012-02-22|archive-date=2012-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120125012755/http://www.allmusic.com/artist/iron-maiden-p4560|dead-url=no}}</ref>和[[威豹樂隊|威豹樂隊]]<ref>{{cite web|language=en|author=Erlewine, Stephen Thomas|url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/def-leppard-p4062|title=Def Leppard|publisher=Allmusic|date=2017-01-20|accessdate=2012-02-22|archive-date=2012-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120522024940/http://www.allmusic.com/artist/def-leppard-p4062|dead-url=no}}</ref>。鐵娘子的貝斯手和詞曲創作者{{link-en|史提夫·哈里斯|Steve Harris (musician)}}曾表示，鐵娘子「沉重」的音樂特質，靈感是來自黑色安息日、深紫和齊柏林飛船<ref>{{cite web|language=en|url=http://legacy.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=27275|title=IRON MAIDEN Bassist Talks About His Technique And Influences|publisher=Blabbermouth|accessdate=2012-02-26|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120526014836/http://legacy.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=27275|archivedate=2012-05-26}}</ref>。

