=== 搖滾名人堂 ===
{{Quote box|width=25em|align=right|quote=“在我九歲時，深紫就改變了我的人生。四十年來幾乎沒有例外，包括我在內的每一支硬式搖滾樂團，只要追溯我們的根源和血統，最終都會導向黑色安息日、齊柏林飛船和深紫。在我長大的地方，或是北美以外的其他地方，所有人的地位和影響力都是平等的。在我心深處，我知道世界上有數百萬個樂迷跟我一樣納悶 — 為什麼這麼久了，深紫還沒有進入搖滾名人堂？”|source=<small>—— [[金屬製品|金屬製品]]的鼓手[[拉爾斯·烏爾里希|拉爾斯·烏爾里希]]，在2016年引介深紫列名搖滾名人堂時的致詞</small><ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/read-lars-ulrichs-passionate-deep-purple-rock-hall-induction-20160408 |title=Read Lars Ulrich's Passionate Deep Purple Rock Hall Induction |last=Grow |first=Kory |publisher=Rolling Stone |date=2016-04-08 |accessdate=2016-05-04 |archive-date=2018-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612144154/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/read-lars-ulrichs-passionate-deep-purple-rock-hall-induction-20160408 |dead-url=no }}</ref>}}
在2012年10月之前，深紫從未被提名進入[[搖滾名人堂|搖滾名人堂]]（他們自1993年起便符合被選資格），直到2012年才開始被提名<ref name="BillboardRHOF">{{cite web|language=en|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/474803/rush-deep-purple-public-enemy-nominated-for-rock-hall-of-fame|title=Rush, Deep Purple, Public Enemy Nominated for Rock Hall of Fame|publisher=Billboard|accessdate=2012-10-11|archive-date=2020-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200922104646/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/474803/rush-deep-purple-public-enemy-nominated-for-rock-hall-of-fame|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|language=en|author=Andy Greene|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/rush-public-enemy-deep-purple-nominated-for-rock-and-roll-hall-of-fame-20121004|title=Rush, Public Enemy, Deep Purple Nominated for Rock and Roll Hall of Fame|publisher=Rolling Stone|date=2012-10-04|accessdate=2012-10-11|archive-date=2017-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171124050225/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/rush-public-enemy-deep-purple-nominated-for-rock-and-roll-hall-of-fame-20121004|dead-url=no}}</ref>。第一次的提名落選<ref>{{cite web|language=en|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/music/posts/la-et-ms-rock-hall-induction-rush-randy-newman-donna-summer-2013-rock-hall-inductees-20121211,0,2611512.story?track=rss&utm_source=feedburner&utm_medium=feed&utm_campaign=Feed%3A+PopHiss+(Pop+%26+Hiss+Music+Blog)|title=Rush, Randy Newman, Donna Summer among 2013 Rock Hall inductees|publisher=[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]|accessdate=2012-12-12|archive-date=2013-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131025132809/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/music/posts/la-et-ms-rock-hall-induction-rush-randy-newman-donna-summer-2013-rock-hall-inductees-20121211,0,2611512.story?track=rss&utm_source=feedburner&utm_medium=feed&utm_campaign=Feed%3A+PopHiss+(Pop+%26+Hiss+Music+Blog)|dead-url=no}}</ref>，吻的貝斯手[[吉恩·西蒙斯|吉恩·西蒙斯]]和匆促樂團的貝斯手[[蓋迪·李|蓋迪·李]]表示，深紫顯然應該列入搖滾名人堂<ref name="Martin Kielty">{{cite news |language=en |title=Rush, Deep Purple finally nominated for Rock and Roll Hall of Fame |author=Martin Kielty |date=2012-10-04 |work=Classic Rock |url=http://www.classicrockmagazine.com/news/rush-deep-purple-finally-nominated-for-rock-and-roll-hall-of-fame/ |accessdate=2017-02-23 |archive-date=2014-02-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140223034827/http://www.classicrockmagazine.com/news/rush-deep-purple-finally-nominated-for-rock-and-roll-hall-of-fame/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/geddy-lee-on-rushs-rock-and-roll-hall-of-fame-induction-well-show-up-smiling-20121211 |title=Geddy Lee on Rush's Rock and Roll Hall of Fame Induction: 'We'll Show Up Smiling |work=Rolling Stone |accessdate=2012-12-12 |archive-date=2012-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121211202809/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/geddy-lee-on-rushs-rock-and-roll-hall-of-fame-induction-well-show-up-smiling-20121211 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在此之前，就有許多音樂人抗議深紫沒有進入搖滾名人堂。{{link-en|托托合唱團|Toto (band)}}的吉他手{{link-en|史蒂夫‧路卡瑟|Steve Lukather}}說：「[[帕蒂·史密斯|帕蒂·史密斯]]都列名了，深紫卻沒有是怎麼回事？每個小孩學彈吉他的第一首歌是什麼？深紫的〈水上煙〉！這樣還進不了？搖滾名人堂已經失去它的格調了，就是因為這種離譜的遺漏」<ref>{{cite web|language=en|url=http://www.futurerocklegends.com/blog_files/Toto_told_Jann_Wenner.html|title=Toto told Jann Wenner to "stick it up his|publisher=Future Rock Legends|accessdate=2012-12-12|archive-date=2020-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201118052638/https://www.futurerocklegends.com/blog_files/Toto_told_Jann_Wenner.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。槍與玫瑰吉他手[[史萊許|史萊許]]也表達了他的驚訝和異議：「提名的名單令人難以置信，對我來說深紫是非常偉大的，你們怎麼能不把深紫列入？」<ref>{{cite web|language=en|author=Jane Stevenson|date=2012-03-23|url=http://m.torontosun.com/2012/03/23/slash-plays-to-canadian-crowd?noimage=true|title=Slash plays to Canadian Crowd|work=Toronto Sun|accessdate=2012-04-27|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131016080737/http://m.torontosun.com/2012/03/23/slash-plays-to-canadian-crowd?noimage=true|archivedate=2013-10-16}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|language=en|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/exclusive-slash-on-closing-the-book-on-guns-n-roses-at-the-hall-of-fame-20120425|title=Slash on Closing the Book on Guns 'N' Roses at the Hall of Fame|work=Rolling Stone|accessdate=2012-04-27|archive-date=2017-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171024152705/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/exclusive-slash-on-closing-the-book-on-guns-n-roses-at-the-hall-of-fame-20120425|dead-url=no}}</ref>。金屬製品成員[[詹姆斯·海特菲爾德|詹姆斯·海特菲爾德]]、[[拉爾斯·烏爾里希|拉爾斯·烏爾里希]]和[[柯克·哈米特|柯克·哈米特]]也不斷遊說委員會將深紫列名<ref>{{cite web|language=en|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/metallica-want-to-avoid-drama-of-a-van-halen-at-rock-and-roll-hall-of-fame-induction-20090115|title=Metallica Want to Avoid "Drama of a Van Halen" at Rock and Roll Hall of Fame Induction|work=Rolling Stone|accessdate=2012-02-28|archive-date=2017-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171024152557/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/metallica-want-to-avoid-drama-of-a-van-halen-at-rock-and-roll-hall-of-fame-induction-20090115|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Kirk Hammett">{{cite web |language = en|title=Metallica Guitarist: 'Deep Purple Definitely Belongs in the Rock and Roll Hall of Game' |date=2012-10-17 |work=blabbermouth.net |url=http://www.blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=180969|accessdate=2016-02-23}}</ref>。2014年4月9日，在《滾石》雜誌的採訪中，烏爾里希表示：「我只有兩個字要說，『深紫』。我很認真，各位，『深紫』這兩個簡單的英語單字」<ref>{{cite news |language=en |title=Metallica's Lars Ulrich on the Rock Hall – 'Two Words: Deep Purple' |publisher=Rolling Stone |url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/metallicas-lars-ulrich-on-the-rock-hall-two-words-deep-purple-20140409/ |last=Grow |first=Kory |date=2014-04-09 |accessdate=2015-10-15 |archive-date=2017-06-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170625122045/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/metallicas-lars-ulrich-on-the-rock-hall-two-words-deep-purple-20140409 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2015年，[[世界摔角娛樂|世界摔角娛樂]]明星[[克里斯·傑利可|克里斯·傑利可]]說：「沒有深紫的名人堂就是屁蛋名人堂，顯然幕後有令人反感的力量不想讓他們進去」<ref>{{cite news|language=en|title=Chris Jericho huge Hall of Fame rant 2015|url=https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=v2L9Me9ZzaI|agency=[[YouTube|YouTube]]|date=2015-10-19|accessdate=2017-02-23|archive-date=2016-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160302045042/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v2L9Me9ZzaI&gl=US&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

為了回應音樂界的疑慮，搖滾名人堂基金會董事兼首席執行長{{link-en|喬爾·派瑞斯曼|Joel Peresman}}表示：「搖滾的定義對每個人來說都是不同的」<ref name="Martin Kielty"/>。深紫的貝斯手羅傑·格洛弗透漏，深紫將來可能會拒絕搖滾名人堂的邀請，這個「美國機構」讓樂團成員覺得「有點矛盾」，他說：「有個委員說，深紫當年只不過是好運而已，這種想法實在是太過庸俗了」<ref name="Guardian">{{cite news |language=en |title=Roger Glover: Deep Purple 'ambivalent' over Hall of Fame call-up |author=Sean Michaels |work=[[衛報|衛報]] |url=https://www.theguardian.com/music/2014/sep/04/roger-glover-deep-purple-ambivalent-hall-of-fame |date=2014-12-04 |accessdate=2017-02-23 |archive-date=2020-07-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200729111938/https://www.theguardian.com/music/2014/sep/04/roger-glover-deep-purple-ambivalent-hall-of-fame |dead-url=no }}</ref>。主唱伊恩·吉蘭也回應說：「我這一生都反體制，我知道他們內部說我們只是歪打正著。這（搖滾名人堂）不是為了樂迷而設，而是為了一些嚼[[雪茄|雪茄]]、談論利益交換的人準備的」<ref>{{cite news |language=en |title=Deep Purple – Ian Gillan: 'I Don't Expect Heavy Rock's Finest To Get Knighthoods' |date=2013-05-19 |work=Contactmusic.com |url=http://www.contactmusic.com/news/ian-gillan-i-don-t-expect-heavy-rock-s-finest-to-get-knighthoods_3672866 |accessdate=2017-02-23 |archive-date=2014-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141105222642/http://www.contactmusic.com/news/ian-gillan-i-don-t-expect-heavy-rock-s-finest-to-get-knighthoods_3672866 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年10月16日，深紫再度被提名進入名人堂，但最終未能入選<ref name="RS 2013">{{cite web|language=en|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/nirvana-kiss-hall-and-oates-nominated-for-rock-and-roll-hall-of-fame-20131016|title=Nirvana, Kiss, Hall and Oates Nominated for Rock and Roll Hall of Fame|work=Rolling Stone|date=2013-10-16|accessdate=2017-02-23|archive-date=2016-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160902070929/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/nirvana-kiss-hall-and-oates-nominated-for-rock-and-roll-hall-of-fame-20131016|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Guardian"/>。

2015年4月29日，深紫在《滾石》雜誌讀者調查「2016年最應該進入搖滾名人堂的音樂人」中排名第一<ref>{{cite news |language=en |title=Readers Poll: 10 Acts That Should Enter the Hall of Fame in 2016 |publisher=Rolling Stone |url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/lists/readers-poll-10-acts-that-should-enter-the-hall-of-fame-in-2016-20150429 |last=Green |first=Andy |date=2015-04-29 |accessdate=2015-10-15 |archive-date=2018-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180614214144/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/lists/readers-poll-10-acts-that-should-enter-the-hall-of-fame-in-2016-20150429 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同年10月，深紫第三次獲得提名<ref name="RS 2015">{{cite news|language=en|title=Vote for the 2016 Rock and Roll Hall of Fame Inductees|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/vote-for-the-2016-rock-and-roll-hall-of-fame-inductees-20151008|publisher=Rolling Stone|date=2015-10-18|accessdate=2017-02-23|archive-date=2018-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180618213222/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/vote-for-the-2016-rock-and-roll-hall-of-fame-inductees-20151008|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年12月，深紫入圍2016年度候選名單，搖滾名人堂發表聲明：「沒有深紫的名人堂是空洞的，現在是圓滿的時刻。在硬式搖滾和重金屬音樂中，齊柏林飛船、黑色安息日與深紫是[[三位一體|三位一體]]的宗師級樂團」<ref name="Rock Hall 2016">{{cite news|language=en|title=NWA, Deep Purple and Chicago enter Hall of Fame|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-35119852|publisher=英國廣播公司|date=2015-12-17|accessdate=2017-02-23|archive-date=2021-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210315115250/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-35119852|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年4月8日，深紫當選、正式列入搖滾名人堂，該機構宣布以下成員被列入：{{link-en|伊恩·佩斯|Ian Paice}}、[[瓊·洛德|瓊·洛德]]、[[瑞奇·布萊克摩爾|瑞奇·布萊克摩爾]]、{{link-en|羅傑·格洛弗|Roger Glover}}、{{link-en|伊恩·吉蘭|Ian Gillan}}、{{link-en|羅德·艾文斯|Rod Evans}}、[[大衛·科弗代爾|大衛·科弗代爾]]和{{link-en|葛倫·休斯|Glenn Hughes}}。被排除在外的成員是{{link-en|尼克·辛博|Nick Simper}}、{{link-en|湯米·波林|Tommy Bolin}}、{{link-en|喬·林·特納|Joe Lynn Turner}}、[[喬·沙翠亞尼|喬·沙翠亞尼]]、{{link-en|史提夫·莫爾斯|Steve Morse}}和{{link-en|唐·艾瑞|Don Airey}}<ref name="Rock Hall 2016Gillan">{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/deep-purple-singer-rock-hall-band-member-exclusions-are-very-silly-20151221 |title=Deep Purple Singer: Rock Hall Band Member Exclusions Are 'Very Silly' |publisher=Rolling Stone |last=Reed |first=Ryan |date=2015-12-21 |accessdate=2017-02-23 |archive-date=2017-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171124132029/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/deep-purple-singer-rock-hall-band-member-exclusions-are-very-silly-20151221 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。對此結果，吉蘭表示名人堂此舉非常獨斷：「我的感激之情已打了折扣，吉他手史提夫·莫爾斯和鍵盤手唐·艾瑞都已經在深紫待了很久。這樣做非常愚蠢，就像有個老朋友邀請你參加婚體，結果卻只准你和離婚十年的前妻赴宴，而不准和現任妻子一起去」<ref name="Rock Hall 2016Gillan"/>。

在頒獎典禮舉行之前，吉蘭宣布禁止葛倫·休斯、大衛·科弗代爾、羅德·艾文斯、瑞奇·布萊克摩爾和深紫一起在典禮上登台：「因為這些成員不是當前的樂團陣容。史提夫·莫爾斯和唐·艾瑞將會出席登台，這是對他們倆人的基本尊重」<ref>{{cite web|language=en|author=Michael Gallucci|url=http://ultimateclassicrock.com/ian-gillan-deep-purple-rock-hall/|title=Ian Gillan Comments on Deep Purple's Decision to Perform With Current Lineup at Rock Hall Induction|publisher=Ultimate Classic Rock|date=2016-02-19|accessdate=2017-02-23|archive-date=2020-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201114122504/https://ultimateclassicrock.com/ian-gillan-deep-purple-rock-hall/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。典禮當天，八位列名成員中，有五位出席。眾所矚目的布萊克摩爾缺席，他在[[Facebook|Facebook]]粉絲專頁上表示：「對於入選感到榮幸，並考慮出席。直到收到來自深紫經紀人{{link-en|布魯斯·佩恩 (經紀人)|Bruce Payne|布魯斯·佩恩}}的拒絕信，因此我將不會出席。真誠感謝所有支持我的樂迷」<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/deep-purple-guitarist-ritchie-blackmore-wont-attend-hall-of-fame-ceremony-20160219 |title=Deep Purple Guitarist Ritchie Blackmore Won't Attend Hall of Fame Ceremony |publisher=Rolling Stone |last=Greene |first=Andy |date=2016-02-16 |accessdate=2017-02-23 |archive-date=2017-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201032655/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/deep-purple-guitarist-ritchie-blackmore-wont-attend-hall-of-fame-ceremony-20160219 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而，在名人堂的採訪中，吉蘭表示他曾親自邀請布萊克摩爾出席，但不是在舞台上演出。第一任主唱羅德·艾文斯已經在三十多年前就消失於音樂界，也未出席。而瓊·洛德已經逝世，由遺孀代為接受加冕。深紫當前的「Mark VIII」陣容表演了〈公路之星〉，之後洛德的照片出現在大螢幕上，樂團繼續演奏〈安靜〉和傳奇名曲〈水上煙〉。

